UID:best-kept-secret-2026-fdce699295ea760f@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T120000Z
DTEND:20260612T150000Z
SUMMARY:DJ St. Paul
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:The Floor manager who lets it all happen\n\nDJ St. Paul aka the
  pundit behind Pop-O-Matic\, aka the honcho of Let It Happen\, aka the chi
 ef facilitator of Best Kept Secret's The Floor.Paul isn’t a floor manage
 r like those at normal work environments\; it’s all play in his book. Ev
 ery year he invites an uncanny list of guests from all corners and crevice
 s of the music world – blasting the biggest hits\, the most vital niches
  & subcultures\, the juiciest of deep cuts\, and everything inbetween at T
 he Floor. It’s quite literally all hands on deck when St. Paul’s your 
 host – an exploration of pure dance-floor euphoria in all its vast devia
 tions. An individual eternally ready for both the moment and the sound.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-3f774bcd0ffcc276@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T150000Z
DTEND:20260612T160000Z
SUMMARY:Rimini Express (Vinyl Only Italo Set)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:A devoted missionary for all things Italo\n\nNo fake moustaches
  or other indulging clichés on this guy’s body. Rimini Express carries 
 the Italo experience in his heart.\nIn the club\, with his radioshow or ev
 en via lectures\, the gingerly rising DJ is spreading his obsessive passio
 n for the depths of Italy’s ever more popular soundtrack. Strictly on vi
 nyl of course. Hop on the Rimini Express and try his love beat by beat.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
