BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-6ebdedfb121599a5@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T170000Z
DTEND:20260612T180000Z
SUMMARY:Kaat van Stralen (DJ Set)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Genre-defying punk band playing first ever DJ set.\n\nLinguisti
 c uproar\, crackling beats\, biting guitar riffs and thunderous bass lines
 .\nThe Belgian power generator Kaat van Stralen is taking our country stag
 e by stage. “Stop Met Wenen” has become the national anthem and her fe
 minist message wrapped in genre-defying music feels more urgent than ever.
  After their much loved show Best Kept Secret 2025\, Kaat and her band wil
 l travel back again to the festival\, but this time for a first ever DJ se
 t. Riotous punk? Baywatch aerobics? The Floor can’t wait!
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
