UID:best-kept-secret-2026-308fd61eec135304@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T233000Z
DTEND:20260613T003000Z
SUMMARY:Iliassopdebeat
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Hey girls\, hey boys\, superstar producers\, here we go!\n\nOne
  of the most celebrated producers of the wild wild west.\nMaking beats at 
 his first Moroccan holidays. Making beats at school. Making beats for brea
 kfast. As a producer and hitmaker Iliassopdebeat wears titles such as “T
 he Dutch Timbaland” like it’s an old pair of sneakers. As a DJ there i
 s a whole new territory opening up. Fresh off his performance with lyrical
  counterpart MULA B on Stage Two\, Illias will bring the noize like tomorr
 ow never happens.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
