DTEND:20260614T124500Z
SUMMARY:Sheyma (Live)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:A commanding voice blending Western and Arab culture\n\nBreatht
 aking singer with a live performance that blends electronic beats and trad
 itional Arab music.\nOne of the crowd favourites at the recent edition of 
 the Grauzone Festival\, Sheyma Rochdi is destroying boring borders with he
 r sound\, one as intimate as it is riotous. A voice that needs to be heard
  to be believed. Sheyma's music is inspired by influences from different g
 enres of Moroccan music such as Gnawa music\, Moroccan Chaabi mixed with A
 rabic alternative. While her vocals are connected to traditions of Arabic 
 music\, the structures of the songs are very remote from its codes. True f
 reedom this way lies.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
