DTSTART:20260614T143000Z
DTEND:20260614T153000Z
SUMMARY:Girls to the Front (DJ Set)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Modern day riot girl representing FLINTA punk\n\nBibi Fay Banni
 nk\, an 18 year old feminist punk fan with a plan\, started Girls To The F
 ront to represent the FLINTA community.\nTaking inspiration from the Riot 
 Grrrl movement this grew out to a compilation of FLINTA-fronted punk bands
 \, an extensive club tour plus interdisciplinary events with poetry\, film
  talks and panels. This DJ-set will show the depths of FLINTA* punk. From 
 the Dutch underground scene to Pakistani-American wave to Javanese electro
  Bibi will celebrate identities through punk as a lifestyle.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
