DTEND:20260614T200000Z
SUMMARY:Aili & Orson (Japanese DJ Set)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Electro-pop duo visiting Japanese roots in unique DJ Set\n\nAil
 i is a Belgium-Japanese electro-pop duo consisting of Aili Maruyama and Or
 son Wouters.\nTheir instant musical chemistry led to a playful and spontan
 eous approach to songwriting\, combining electronic beats\, samples\, and 
 Aili's unique blend of Japanese vocals. A highlight within the recent outp
 ut of the infamous Eskimo Recordings label. Who needs a game of football a
 gainst the Japanese when you dance to their music too!!
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
