SUMMARY:Mr. Cutts
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Influential British producer taking social media by storm(zy)\n
 \nMr. Cutts\, London producer and music’s most instarational guide\, vis
 its The Floor.\nCLASH Magazine wrote about Owen Cutts – specifically his
  productions for artists like Stormzy\, Jgrrey and Jacob Collier – that 
 he has been involved with some of the best British releases of the past de
 cade. His endless love for the beats\, as well as the originals\, is the d
 riving force behind his immensely popular insta-account. Mr. Cutts flying 
 over for one hour at The Floor? Dusty Springfield singing 'Believe me beli
 eve me!'
