SUMMARY:Ofra
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Together in electric dreams with the finest selection of Synthp
 op\, Postpunk & EBM\n\nFew DJ’s walk the line between electronic music a
 nd your favorite bands as gently as Ofra does.\nYes\, she co-founded the R
 otterdam-based online radio station Operator and runs music platform / lab
 el Yarrow Balle. But as a DJ she is nothing but a travel agent\, guiding u
 s past the depths of synth pop\, wave\, acid\, postpunk\, EBM and shoegaze
  to emotional heights. No better way to start the night than with the elec
 tric dreams of Ofra.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
